<span style=\"--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379\"> admin</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379\"> /etc/</span></span></code></pre>\n</div><p><code v-pre>-v</code> 过滤包含某个词的行，即 <code v-pre>grep</code> 的逆操作。</p>\n<div class=\"language-bash\" data-highlighter=\"shiki\" data-ext=\"bash\" data-title=\"bash\" style=\"--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#abb2bf;--shiki-light-bg:#FAFAFA;--shiki-dark-bg:#282c34\"><pre v-pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes one-light one-dark-pro vp-code\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#A0A1A7;--shiki-light-font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#7F848E;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic\"># 显示所有包含 vim，但不包含 grep 的行</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#4078F2;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF\">$</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379\"> ps</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF\"> | </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#4078F2;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF\">grep</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379\"> vim</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF\"> | </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#4078F2;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF\">grep</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#986801;--shiki-dark:#D19A66\"> -v</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379\"> grep</span></span></code></pre>\n</div>","env":{"base":"/","filePath":"/Users/carson/Desktop/Mister-Hope.github.io-main/src/linux/bash/archives/commands/grep.md","filePathRelative":"linux/bash/archives/commands/grep.md","frontmatter":{"date":"2020-06-04T00:00:00.000Z"},"sfcBlocks":{"template":{"type":"template","content":"<template><h1 id=\"grep\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#grep\"><span>grep</span></a></h1>\n<p><code v-pre>grep</code> 命令用于文件内容的搜索，返回所有匹配的行。</p>\n<div class=\"language-bash\" data-highlighter=\"shiki\" data-ext=\"bash\" data-title=\"bash\" style=\"--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#abb2bf;--shiki-light-bg:#FAFAFA;--shi